      "parameters": {
        "width": 342.9710297084147,
        "height": 601.2740375761717,
        "content": "## 复制此模板开始使用：\n- [Google Sheets](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1efCCzfeUX0AETz2wsULQN90OBCOKK-gBoDaptzcBHdE/edit?usp=sharing)\n\n## 工作流节点文档：\n\n1. [定时触发器](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/core-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.scheduletrigger/)\n2. [按当前日期筛选条目](https://docs.n8n.io/nodes/n8n-nodes-base.code.html)\n3. [Gmail](https://docs.n8n.io/nodes/n8n-nodes-base.gmail.html)\n4. [Google Sheets](https://docs.n8n.io/nodes/n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets.html)\n5. [状态筛选（待发送）](https://docs.n8n.io/nodes/n8n-nodes-base.filter.html)\n6. [设置数据](https://docs.n8n.io/nodes/n8n-nodes-base.set.html)\n7. [合并字段](https://docs.n8n.io/nodes/n8n-nodes-base.merge.html)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
